title: Radio Interview with Cannonball Adderly Jazz Saxaphonist 1975
description: KDKO Soul Radio in Denver did interviews with soul and jazz performers that were in town, and Cannonball was one of them!   This was done in 1975  -- later that same year, Cannonball had a stroke and died, this may have been his last interview.
fulltitle: Radio Interview with Cannonball Adderly Jazz Saxaphonist 1975
